The paper proposes a new memory architecture for semantic visual navigation agents, which involves probabilistic relation graphs over semantic entities. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper involves probabilistic modeling and efficient planning, which are relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY).
